# filter-scan-to-bitmap-index

## Description

Migrated to a declarative `.rra` rule (RFC 0090 Phase 2).

## Rewrite

lhs: (filter ?pred (scan ?table))
rhs: (bitmap-index-scan ?table auto ?pred)
when: is_not_const_bool("?pred")
